Alpha,Micro,Systems,AMS,provides,vehicle,tracking,and,asset,security,solutions,that,are,compatible,with,mobile,and,web,based,platforms,AMS,provides,location,aware,technology,that,businesses,can,use,to,track,valuable,items,and,reporting,technology,that,can,be,used,to,leverage,location,data,gathered,as,your,assets,move,from,point,to,point,The,AMS,API,has,a,wide,array,of,methods,for,managing,driver,vehicle,device,and,customer,data,The,operations,offered,by,this,API,represent,the,most,popular,features,from,the,AMS,tracking,applications,and,services,allowing,developers,to,integrate,their,existing,platform,with,AMS,system,This,is,a,SOAP,based,API,that,requires,an,account,with,service,for,access